8
00:00:35,520 --> 00:00:37,799
There are always people who take a different path.

9
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:41,719
It's you who gave me the courage to break free.

10
00:00:41,719 --> 00:00:42,520
Sister Su,

11
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:45,039
