12
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:46,679
which was put out by the wind.

13
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:49,280
Now it's burning again.

14
00:00:49,439 --> 00:00:49,920
Yes.

15
00:00:52,039 --> 00:00:53,359
It's surprising that

16
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:54,920
my mother didn't blame me,

17
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:56,439
but supported me.

18
00:00:57,039 --> 00:00:58,159
No mother wants

19
00:00:58,159 --> 00:00:59,880
