21
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:02,920
Yes.

22
00:01:07,799 --> 00:01:08,319
Yan Ge,

23
00:01:08,959 --> 00:01:10,280
Sister Su and I have discussed it.

24
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:13,239
We'll help you get rid of your slave status.

25
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,719
If she's willing to let me go,

26
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:19,719
