29
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,239
Now that Shen Yuan is on the run,

30
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,439
and we have her weaknesses,

31
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,719
it's worth a try.

32
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:32,239
Hope so.

33
00:01:33,719 --> 00:01:34,920
Don't worry.

34
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:36,959
We're with you.

35
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:39,640
And we have a new member.

36
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:40,560
That is

37
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:41,840
Yunzhou.

38
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:45,840
By the way,

39
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:47,319
I've heard you call him Yunzhou.

40
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,159
Is it his courtesy name?

41
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:49,840
Yes.

42
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:52,840
We've known each other since childhood.

43
00:01:53,319 --> 00:01:56,319
But our families were rivals,

44
00:01:56,519 --> 00:01:57,319
so they didn't

45
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,640
