to be like this.

54
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:17,639
And then?

55
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:19,400
Then,

56
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:23,000
our families competed for a palace market deal,

57
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:24,639
