88
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:36,960
Yunzhou never came to see me again.

89
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:42,080
Do you know that during the day,

90
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:43,960
because we are staying at the Xiao's,

91
00:03:45,039 --> 00:03:46,719
the Xiao family came to question us,

92
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:49,319
