93
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:52,560
Is that true?

94
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:53,840
Why didn't you tell me?

95
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:57,080
That's because

96
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,599
your husband

97
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,840
