104
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:17,759
I dare not think about it.

105
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,079
I know how Yunzhou treats me.

106
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:22,759
But

107
00:04:24,279 --> 00:04:25,959
we can't let go of

108
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:28,160
