113
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:39,319
help my father repay his debts,

114
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,680
and find him.

115
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,759
I want to

116
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:43,839
