125
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:01,959
We will issue a verification certificate.

126
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:04,160
I will seal it for you.

127
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:05,639
If one day

128
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,720
