137
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,439
This world

138
00:05:21,839 --> 00:05:22,600
[is harsh]

139
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,480
[on women,]

140
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:24,959
[but we must]

141
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:27,279
[never devalue ourselves.]

142
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,240
[Meanwhile,]

143
00:05:28,439 --> 00:05:31,040
[we will continue our night clinic and emergency care,]

144
00:05:31,879 --> 00:05:32,879
[serving all, regardless of wealth.]

145
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:35,040
[We hope to create a safe space]

146
