[for women]

147
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,240
[in this world.]

148
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,480
The sufferings in this world

149
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,600
include not only the cold and heat,

150
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,560
but also the darkness of the heart.

151
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,360
What we need to do

152
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,720
is to turn the silent pain

153
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,600
into a powerful counterattack.

154
00:05:52,439 --> 00:05:53,959
We are not only healers,

155
00:05:53,959 --> 00:05:55,399
but also witnesses

156
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:56,839
