157
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,079
I want one.

158
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:00,360
I want one.

159
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,000
I want one too.

160
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,079
Give me one.

161
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:02,759
I'll take one too.

162
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:03,360
Thank you.

163
