192
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,439
Very well.

193
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,040
Then...

194
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,319
Please...

195
00:07:32,439 --> 00:07:33,839
I've heard from my wife

196
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:36,519
that you can help the Shangshu's

197
00:07:36,879 --> 00:07:38,160
