200
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,240
indicating healthy lung function.

201
00:07:46,519 --> 00:07:47,680
You'll have the energy to

202
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,439
raise your child in the future.

203
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:50,680
My Lord.

204
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,720
That's very good.

205
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,920
But I still

206
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,839
have palpitations, insomnia,

207
00:07:58,519 --> 00:07:59,199
and

208
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,000
