214
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:09,959
If the spleen is damaged for a long time,

215
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:11,319
it will consume heart blood,

216
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,240
causing palpitations, insomnia,

217
00:08:13,519 --> 00:08:14,920
and fatigue.

218
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:17,040
You must be overthinking.

219
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,959
You should calm your mind.

220
00:08:18,959 --> 00:08:19,439
Avoid

221
00:08:20,079 --> 00:08:20,560
