224
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:27,240
I have no choice in the matter.

225
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,000
As for your concerns,

226
00:08:29,279 --> 00:08:30,519
you might consider a long-term strategy,

227
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,680
or perhaps

228
00:08:31,879 --> 00:08:33,039
seek allies who share your vision

229
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:34,320
to devise a sound plan.

230
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:37,320
It seems

231
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:38,840
