233
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,919
[It appears that I have unwittingly]

234
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:46,399
[become a pawn of Madam Yin.]

235
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:50,039
I dare not deceive you.

236
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,320
Making incense is true,

237
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,639
and I truly wish

238
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:53,720
to ease your worries.

239
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:58,519
Who are you?

240
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:01,000
My name is Yin Xinyue,

241
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,240
and my father is

242
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,879
Yin Shifeng.

243
00:09:05,559 --> 00:09:06,080
Guards,

244
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,240
