288
00:10:41,279 --> 00:10:43,360
How could he have signed this contract?

289
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:45,799
I don't understand either.

290
00:10:46,639 --> 00:10:47,200
But I

291
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:49,000
have indeed seen Yin Shifeng.

292
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:50,600
When and where?

293
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:51,759
