295
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:56,120
And I haven't found him since.

296
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:58,399
So you mean

297
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:02,559
he faked his death to escape responsibility.

298
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:05,120
This transportation contract

299
00:11:05,759 --> 00:11:07,440
is a deliberate ruse

300
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,159
to create the illusion

301
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:12,279
of being framed.

302
00:11:16,399 --> 00:11:17,840
That's just his speculation.

303
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:20,320
If my father faked his death,

304
00:11:20,559 --> 00:11:22,360
why hasn't he appeared to clarify?

305
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,000
My lord, please see clearly.

306
00:11:25,519 --> 00:11:28,120
If my father wanted to escape responsibility,

307
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:30,720
why would he leave such a flaw?

308
00:11:31,639 --> 00:11:34,799
The imitator must be eager to prove himself

309
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,440
and revealed himself.

310
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:38,879
You said you saw my father,

311
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:40,399
but it may just be someone who looks like him.

312
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,240
It may not be my father.

313
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:44,919
If he's still alive,

314
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,919
how could he leave you alone in Chang'an?

315
00:11:49,159 --> 00:11:50,240
If he's dead,

316
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:53,279
how come we still can't find his body?

317
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,320
Unless

318
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:58,240
he faked his death to escape.

319
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,279
I don't know.

320
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,759
Shen Yuan and Su Erman

321
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,799
must be watched by someone else.

322
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,360
Someone is manipulating this game,

323
00:12:07,879 --> 00:12:09,120
and hasn't shown up yet.

324
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:12,039
If we arrest them now,

325
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,480
all the clues will be interrupted.

326
00:12:15,039 --> 00:12:16,200
I'm still unsure about it,

327
00:12:16,639 --> 00:12:18,320
so I'm here to ask you.

328
00:12:18,879 --> 00:12:19,279
Should we

329
00:12:19,759 --> 00:12:21,320
continue investigating in secret,

330
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,519
or should we arrest them

331
00:12:23,639 --> 00:12:24,679
and hand them over to the Supreme Court?

332
00:12:24,879 --> 00:12:26,279
Have you considered

333
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:27,919
Yin Shifeng's role

334
00:12:28,159 --> 00:12:30,399
in this mutual market?

335
00:12:30,799 --> 00:12:32,559
Although the contract is fake,

336
00:12:32,639 --> 00:12:33,759
without it,

337
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:37,039
something is missing in the mutual market.

338
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:40,399
Transportation.

339
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:44,159
I know what to do now.

340
00:12:44,919 --> 00:12:46,120
Thank you, My Lord.

341
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:51,399
I'll hand over the evidence to the supreme court.

342
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:53,840
But we can't make it public yet.

343
00:12:54,279 --> 00:12:55,879
Because it involves too many people.

344
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:58,600
We need to stay calm.

345
00:12:58,919 --> 00:12:59,840
Jinnuo.

346
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:07,879
My Lord,

347
00:13:08,919 --> 00:13:10,440
have you ever received

348
00:13:10,679 --> 00:13:13,600
a letter of help from Xiao?

349
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,440
Never.

350
00:13:19,159 --> 00:13:21,039
Is there anything else?

351
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,519
My child is no more.

352
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:26,200
It was just a foolish dream of mine.

353
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,720
[It's the women's clinic she runs,]

354
00:13:35,559 --> 00:13:37,320
[the one treating the singing courtesans.]

355
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:37,840
[Yes.]

356
00:13:39,759 --> 00:13:41,200
Isn't she the top performer from the Bright Moon Pavilion?

357
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:43,600
She's seen countless men.

358
00:13:44,039 --> 00:13:45,799
I bet that clinic isn't as clean as it seems.

359
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:47,080
I heard

360
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,799
she even lets that singing courtesan help run it.

361
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,360
What women's clinic treating only ladies?

362
00:13:51,919 --> 00:13:52,360
I think,

363
00:13:52,639 --> 00:13:54,440
it's probably for treating shameful diseases.

364
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:55,360
What are you talking about?

365
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:58,000
If you're sick, go get treated.

366
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,840
If not, stop gossiping.

367
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:01,360
Can't you understand

368
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,600
what we're saying?

369
00:14:03,039 --> 00:14:04,039
The court has laws.

370
00:14:04,559 --> 00:14:06,759
Outcastes can't redeem themselves or run businesses.

371
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:09,039
Let alone the top performer from Bright Moon Pavilion.

372
00:14:10,039 --> 00:14:12,000
Many people have enjoyed her beauty.

373
00:14:13,919 --> 00:14:15,080
Everyone knows that.

374
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:17,639
And it's in our Changle District.

375
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:19,639
Isn't this bringing bad luck to us?

376
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:20,000
I...

377
00:14:22,039 --> 00:14:23,039
We both have important matters.

378
00:14:23,679 --> 00:14:24,399
Don't let these idle words

379
00:14:25,039 --> 00:14:25,679
disturb your mind.

380
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:31,720
Unfortunately, this clinic can only cure diseases.

381
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,879
It can't cure your filthy hearts.

382
00:14:36,639 --> 00:14:37,240
What kind of person are you?

383
00:14:37,919 --> 00:14:38,919
Stop pretending to be noble.

384
00:14:43,559 --> 00:14:44,159
Yan Ge,

385
00:14:44,679 --> 00:14:45,320
what are you doing?

386
00:14:47,159 --> 00:14:48,039
Sister Su,

387
00:14:49,399 --> 00:14:50,320
you're right.

388
00:14:52,120 --> 00:14:54,000
I shouldn't have stayed here from the start.

389
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:55,480
When I'm not around,

390
00:14:57,399 --> 00:14:58,559
take care of yourself.
